&lt;li&gt;cold calls&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;supporting marketing with outbound campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;working charter conferences,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;mining referral networks.&lt;/li&gt;
